@startuml
title UC06 Credential owner が credential または grant を取り消す

actor "Credential owner" as Owner
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore

Owner -> UI: credential または grant 管理画面を開く
UI -> Firestore: owner の credential / grant 一覧を取得
Firestore --> UI: 一覧
UI --> Owner: credential / grant 一覧を表示

Owner -> UI: 取り消す対象を選択して送信
UI -> API: 取り消しを要求
API -> Firestore: credential を無効化\nまたは grant を削除
Firestore --> API: 更新完了
API --> UI: 取り消し成功
UI --> Owner: 反映完了を表示
@enduml
